ygData.msgSnippet: If you try and get rubicite at level 28, no matter how strong your party is, all you are going to do is tick off everyone in CT as you train the stuff through
ygData.messageBody:
If you try and get rubicite at level 28, no matter how strong your party
is, all you are going to do is tick off everyone in CT as you train the
stuff through them running for your lives, if you make it that far. Don't
make a try for the rubicite unless your group is over 30 and at least one
person has done it before. Had that done to me one night in CT every twenty
minutes or so, now I'm up in Najena getting good stuff.

Oglug ~Hand of Chaos~ CT
